    "created_at": "2015-11-27T02:21:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-27T02:21:38Z",
    "body": "As far as I can see, there is a `executable` property in the `asar` header [set on executable files](https://github.com/atom/asar/blob/master/src/filesystem.coffee#L46).\n\nI can get the value of this property for a specific file by using `asar.statFile`. I'll modify this PR to only set execution permissions if this property is set to `true`, which should prevent the edge case where the user didn't set the execution permissions manually and we diverge from usual behaviour by adding it ourselves.\n"
  },
